\left({\sum_{k \mathop = 1}^n \left({a_k + b_k + c_k + d_k}\right)^p}\right)^{1/p} \le \left({\sum_{k \mathop = 1}^n a_k^p}\right)^{1/p} + \left({\sum_{k \mathop = 1}^n b_k^p}\right)^{1/p} + \left({\sum_{k \mathop = 1}^n c_k^p}\right)^{1/p} + \left({\sum_{k \mathop = 1}^n d_k^p}\right)^{1/p}
\sqrt{k^2+(b-l)^2} + \sqrt{l^2 + (a-m)^2} + \sqrt{m^2+(b-n)^2} + \sqrt{n^2+(a-k)^2} \geq \sqrt{(k+(a-m)+m+(a-k))^2+((b-l)+l+(b-n)+n)^2} = 2 \sqrt{a^2+b^2}.
